Subject: [R-SIG-Win] Rtools44 update
Message-ID: <0e7ae230-1053-41ba-8749-edbd90f629fa@gmail.com>

Dear R Windows developers,

an update of Rtools44, the toolchain for R for Windows used by R-devel 
and R 4.4, is available as revision 6335 from

https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/Rtools/rtools44/rtools.html

GCC is updated to 13.3.0 with several patches. HDF5 is now built with 
Fortran support. A number of libraries have been updated to newer versions.

See

https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/Rtools/rtools44/news.html

for more details.

Best
Tomas


